description: '''Natalia Alexandra Guti√©rrez Batista''' (born December 10, 1986), better known by her stage name '''Natti Natasha''' (stylized [[all caps]]), is a [[List of people from the Dominican Republic|Dominican]] singer. She was signed to [[Don Omar]]'s label [[Orfanato Music Group]]. Her debut EP, ''All About Me'', was released on March 28, 2012, by Orfanato Music Group.
